<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>LOVEST THOU ME MORE THAN THESE?</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal Isu A thawhkit nungin,
 Tiberia dila nga mante;
 A sinsakte kawmah A kilak a,
 Zing annek zawh in Peter chuh;
 Zie thu pawimawh hi A dawng tai.

[V2]
 Simon Jona chapa, nang zie haw sangin,
 Kei nei hehpih zawm? (2)
 Simon Jona chapa zie haw sangin,
 Nei hehpih zaw'm? ti'n A dawnga.
 Simon Peter chun a dawnga,
 &quot;Ka hun hehpih hi tih Na he'i (2)
 Aw Lalpa bang cheng Na he a,
 Ka hun hehpih tih na he'i&quot; ti'n.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa'n Simon Peter kawmah,
 &quot;Ka Belam note vak inla;
 Ka Belamte enkawl in nekding pie'n,
 Na naupan lai bang ta puo'n tin,
 Nang thu lo a puih hita'n la.&quot;

[V4]
 3. Ei le Lalpa'n Peter guol in,
 Amah hehph pen di'n ei deih;
 I thilneih I sum-leh-pai bang cheng leh,
 I lunggil I hatnau chengin,
 Amah I hehpih zaw nau em?

[V5]
 &quot;Aw Lalpa ka hun hehpih hi,
 Khawvel lopina cheng sangin;
 Na nasem di'n kipieng ka ting,
 Nanga ding maiin hing ta'ng ka;
 Nei hehpih ziekin kei di'n Na thi a,
 Beimang sa'n hinna ka mu tai;
 Zieziek chun ka damsung chengin
 Bang cheng sangin hun hehpih ka;
 Na Belamte enkawl ing ting,
 Ka hatna leh ka talent cheng;
 Nang di'n pie'ng ka,&quot;
 I ti ngam dem?</lyrics>
<hymn_number>407</hymn_number>
</song>